<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="downstairs-adv">downstairs <strong><em>adv</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /ˌdaʊn'steəz/    美 /ˌdaʊn'sterz/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>在楼下；往楼下：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>He went downstairs to have breakfast.
他下楼吃早饭。</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">真题解析</h2>
<ol>
<li>Rose rushed <strong><em>_</em></strong>_ (向楼下) to answer the door.   （2008 全国）  </li>
</ol>
<p>答案：
1. downstairs  </p></div>